effect:
Bring forth the mighty storms, so that this world shall taste your fury. An arcane master of climate control, once per mission, you can invoke nature’s wrath in an outdoor area, empowering you. Choose one effect in that area for the remainder of the mission:
• STORMS: Lightning strikes the land, your attacks gain +1 to hit and are ELECTRIFIED;
• FIRE: Fire rains from the sky, your attacks deal +2 extra DAMAGE;
• WIND: Strong gusts sweep obstacles away, gain +1 to rolls with REFLEXIVE;
• QUAKES: Jagged formations erupt from the ground to shield you, gain +1 ARMOR. Conjuring natural disasters will always hinder you and your bandmates in some way
- the Referee decides how.
